---
import AnimatedLogo from "./AnimatedLogo.astro";
const today = new Date();
---

<footer
  class="w-full bg-brand-gray mt-auto border-t-[3px] border-brand-red py-10"
>
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10 md:gap-16">
      <!-- Brand Column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="w-48 mb-6 md:mb-8">
          <AnimatedLogo
            mode="static"
            variant="full"
            color="var(--color-brand-black)"
            align="left"
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-medium text-brand-black max-w-lg leading-relaxed"
        >
          Branding Estratégico. Desarrollo Web. Productos Digitales. Ayudamos a
          marcas visionarias a construir su futuro digital con estándares de
          escalabilidad, eficiencia y "lore".
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 opacity-60">
          <a
            href="/complaints-book"
            class="group mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 w-fit border border-brand-black/20 px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-brand-black hover:text-white transition-all duration-300"
            title="Libro de Reclamaciones"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-sans font-900 tracking-tighter"
              >Libro de reclamaciones</span
            >
          </a>
          <p class="text-[9px] font-sans font-bold text-brand-black uppercase">
            Humanoides & Asociados es una marca de DSIGN S.A.C
          </p>
          <p class="text-[9px] font-sans font-medium text-brand-black">
            RUC: 20609948257
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Socials & Copyright Column -->
      <div class="md:col-start-4 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div class="mb-8 md:text-right">
          <h3
            class="text-xs font-sans font-900 text-brand-black tracking-normal mb-6 border-b-2 border-brand-black pb-2 hidden md:inline-block md:ml-auto uppercase"
          >
            Links de Interés
          </h3>
          <nav
            class="flex flex-row md:flex-col justify-center md:justify-end gap-6 md:gap-1"
          >
            <a
              href="https://instagram.com/humanoidesyasociados"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-sm font-sans font-bold text-brand-black hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity tracking-normal"
              >Instagram</a
            >
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/79018424/admin/dashboard/"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-sm font-sans font-bold text-brand-black hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity tracking-normal"
              >LinkedIn</a
            >

            <a
              href="/privacy"
              class="text-sm font-sans font-bold text-brand-black hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity tracking-normal"
              >Legal</a
            >
          </nav>
        </div>

        <div
          class="md:text-right text-center flex flex-col items-center md:items-end"
        >
          <p
            class="text-sm font-sans font-bold text-brand-black tracking-normal leading-relaxed mb-2"
          >
            &copy; {today.getFullYear()} Humanoides & Asociados.
          </p>
          <span
            id="disclamer"
            class="text-[9px] leading-tight text-brand-black block ml-auto mr-auto md:mr-0 md:ml-auto max-w-xs md:max-w-none opacity-60"
          >
            Todos los derechos reservados. Esta marca no tiene vinculación
            comercial, legal ni editorial con "Les Humanoïdes Associés".
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
